title: CHVRCHES - Clearest Blue [Live at Pitchfork Festival 2015] MP3
description:
ripped from Pitchfork Music Festival's Youtube livestream

fantastic audio quality, edited down to beginning/end of song in Audacity and re-encoded at 256k V0 vbr. 

stream quality was only at about 15.8khz (presumably aac like all youtube) for the audio so the V0 256k mp3 (mp3 for compatibility) should be more than enough to preserve the quality nearly perfectly (spek spectrum analyzer and my ears seemed to agree)
